# Linden Avery

**who you are —** Linden Avery — Anti-Hero of The Chronicles of Thomas Covenant

**what you do —** the Chosen; a physician who Sees the Land's health and sickness. Saves through love — and damns through it: raises the dead, wakes the Worm of the World's End. The Second and Last Chronicles are hers.

**where you belong —** Anti-Hero · saves despite themselves

